* * * * * * * * * * BreakFloor_Concrete * * * * * * * * * * 

Made by Rokusho

Rokusho39@Hotmail.com


To install, place .BSP file into the maps folder of CS:S.

A quick and simple map I found in my HDD that I never
released.  After a quick tidy up of it, I decided to 
release the map fully.  Enjoy.

This is not up to my usual standard, as I said, I found it
on my HDD when cleaning up.  It plays a lto faster than
a normal breakfloor map as the blocks break easier, but
there are more of them.  Seeing as the compile log stated
I had over %106 physics.
